cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.MM, cs.HC

This paper deals with web tracking, which is a security and privacy concern, making cs.CR (Security and Privacy) the most likely category. The paper also involves crawling webpages and analyzing behavior, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The use of invisible pixels and image analysis suggests cs.MM (Multimedia) as another possible category. Finally, the paper discusses user tools and their limitations, which relates to cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
